# 1. 必须立刻修改的主张与文字

## 1.1 标题需要降调

当前方向如果继续使用 “neural operator” 会引来 ML 审稿人对 operator learning 理论、泛化边界、函数空间映射的更高要求。你们现有证据更像 **phase-only optical frontend + digital reconstruction**。

建议标题：

> **A phase-only diffractive frontend for hybrid self-calibrated imaging through dynamic aberrations**

避免：

* “all-optical”
* “neural operator” 作为核心标题词
* “robust natural-image imaging”
* “hardware-tolerant diffractive system”

---

## 1.2 摘要必须降调

摘要中不能把 proxy natural-image 和 proxy tolerance 放得像最终现实性验证。建议摘要主线改为：

```text
Dynamic aberrations turn coherent image formation into a time-varying inverse problem whose state is not directly available at measurement time. We study whether a fixed phase-only diffractive frontend can encode calibration-sensitive information before digital reconstruction. The tested system is hybrid optical-digital: a phase-only diffractive stack is followed by intensity detection and a fixed-capacity ridge reconstruction stage. Under a pre-registered dual-ledger benchmark separating held-out aberrations from held-out object families, the phase-only frontend achieved the largest average gain across the two ledgers, but the effect was strongly regime-dependent. The gain was large for held-out aberrations and modest under held-out object-family shift, where a reference-PSF deconvolution baseline remained stronger. Project-local proxy natural-image stress tests further showed that transfer beyond synthetic ledgers requires training-distribution alignment. Engineering perturbation tests identified phase-mask quantization and lateral displacement as dominant vulnerabilities; robust-mask training mitigated first-order quantization and 1 px shift but not larger displacement. These results support a bounded conclusion: a physically constrained diffractive frontend can improve average restoration under dynamic aberrations in a hybrid pipeline, while broader natural-image and hardware claims require stronger validation.
```

---

## 1.3 全文替换高风险措辞

| 当前/风险措辞                            | 建议替换                                                             |
| ---------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------- |
| all-optical reconstruction         | hybrid optical-digital reconstruction                            |
| lightweight digital reconstruction | fixed-capacity digital ridge reconstruction stage                |
| natural-image validation           | project-local proxy natural-image stress test                    |
| hardware robustness                | first-order simulated tolerance diagnosis                        |
| phase-only stack is best           | phase-only stack provides the best average dual-ledger trade-off |
| robust to fabrication errors       | partly tolerant to selected simulated perturbations              |
| neural operator                    | diffractive frontend / hybrid computational optics operator      |

